We are one year old! And in honor of the first birthday we present Tappsk 2.0 Accelerate Your Productivity Running a business and developing habits is by no means the easiest thing to do so we decided to reinvent the wheel and help you in this endeavor! What s new Productivity Rating Find out how productive you are relative to others. Statistics Track the progress of tasks and habits. Recommendations The icing on the cake we have collected the most useful materials and articles for you and will constantly update them. Start time of the day Check off tasks and habits after midnight without changing the date.
This is the final version with minor fixes before the 2.0 release which is scheduled for November 1st.
Some changes that are needed before Tappsk 2.0 is released

Editing bugs.

Let s continue with the edits: When a reminder is set for tomorrow the task date now automatically changes Links in the description work stably The application crashed if you deleted all lists Fixed a bug with saving subtasks Corrected the layout of the diary on large screens If the name of the task changed push notifications came with the old one done Made animation of habits

Thank you very much for your feedback! Corrected habit push notifications and linked them to execution. Now if a habit is marked in advance the notification will not come again Fixed a bug with regular tasks. Previously a copy was not created if they were executed from a push or from a widget
Editing bugs.
New settings: Adding a task to the beginning or end of the day Select the default list Custom reminders: now you can set the number of notifications and their interval

Well half a year has passed and we have settings : And they will be actively updated! Now we have done: sounds changing the language setting up a badge spotlight and fixed widgets.
We added two widgets: for tasks and habits.

And now we re done! We completed a complete code refactoring which significantly increased the speed and optimization of Tappsk. Now the application works equally quickly with both 1 task and 10 000 a huge bunch of bugs related to application crashes and other unpleasant moments have been fixed. And most importantly now we can add new features with greater ease and will be ready to delight you with cool innovations in April!

We receive a lot of feedback and wishes and of course we want to implement them. We are currently refactoring and optimizing the application to easily add new functionality.
